{
  "stem": "5248.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was enough of dairy products and also vegetables and fruit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a wooded area.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a lot of various berries that were collected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was still an open market, so you could go and buy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in school, that-- they were the last years of school, so I was thinking more, you know, that after the school, most of the kids do go to university.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had to work hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was helping me with-- we were thinking-- I was thinking to apply for mathematics, something like that, which was kind a neutral.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We became aware of how vulnerable people are in Russia in various positions, that they could be in a high position one day and then the next-- and then-- and then they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody knows why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So mathematics seemed to be-- algebra, or maybe physics, or whatever, seemed to be a safe profession.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I-- the war started-- I was just about to finish the high school when the war started.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- officially I didn't ever finish it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was when-- when this war between Poland-- between Russia and Germany started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was called Barbarossa, Operation Barbarossa after this pirate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because things dramatically changed overnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dubno is located on the main road between Lwow and Kiev.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This road was actually-- it was always a very bad road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Russians built it to a new road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the road that German tanks used to go to Kiev, because it went Lwow, Dubno, Rowne, and then into the Kiev.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before, it was just, in spring or in fall with rain, the road was very hard to get through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But now they put-- it was only two lane.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
